== 飼養情況 ==
與其它[[蟒屬|蟒蛇]]比較，球蟒的體型較為細小，性情亦較溫和，是相當受歡迎的寵物蛇類。<ref name="MSNG">。[http://groups.msn.com/BallPythons/ballpythons2.msnw Ball Pythons, Selection and Maintenance] {{Wayback|url=http://groups.msn.com/BallPythons/ballpythons2.msnw |date=20070427171642 }} at [http://groups.msn.com/ MSN Groups] {{Wayback|url=http://groups.msn.com/ |date=20090221022437 }}</ref>初生幼蛇可能較具侵略性，但只要自小讓牠們常與人類接觸便可以有效地減低其戾性。從野外捕獲的球蟒較難照料，由於生活氣候差異等因素的影響，球蟒容易被[[寄生|寄生]]生物影響，危害健康。球蟒壽命大約有20至40歲，目前紀錄中最長壽的球蟒有48年的壽命。<ref name="NERD">[http://www.newenglandreptile.com/CareBall.html Ball python] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070113180642/http://www.newenglandreptile.com/CareBall.html |date=2007-01-13 }} at [http://www.newenglandreptile.com/ NERD Herpetocultural Library] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newenglandreptile.com/ |date=20070115201811 }}</ref><ref name="AZOO">[http://www.alaskazoo.org/reptilehome.htm Making Responsible Choices When Considering a Reptile as a Pet] {{Wayback|url=http://www.alaskazoo.org/reptilehome.htm |date=20080311082323 }} at [http://www.alaskazoo.org/ The Alaska Zoo] {{Wayback|url=http://www.alaskazoo.org/ |date=20210224145929 }}</ref>

== 与人类的关系 ==
球蟒與[[西非|西非]][[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]地區[[伊博族|伊博族]]的傳統神話有一定關係。當地人認為球蟒近貼大地行動的特性，是[[地球|地球]]的象徵。儘管伊博族中有很多[[基督教|基督教]]信徒，一些誤闖民居的球蟒仍會得到當地人的重視及悉心照顧。球蟒能在伊博族間肆意遊走，若果有球蟒意外死去，伊博族群更會為牠們設置棺木，立墳墓，甚至為其舉行小型喪禮。<ref>Hambly, Wilfrid Dyson; Laufer, Berthold (1931).[http://www.archive.org/details/serpentworshipin211hamb "Serpent worship"]. Fieldiana Anthropology 21 (1).</ref>

